    "answer_id" : 9163908,
    "question_id" : 1302605,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have this little toy, that also deals with non generic interfaces.\nI'm OK with it throwing a ClassCastException if feed wrong (OK and happy)</p>\n\n<pre><code>public class TypeUtil {\n    public static long castToLong(Object o) {\n        Number n = (Number) o;\n        return n.longValue();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2310590,
      "reputation" : 2997,
      "user_id" : 2028803,
      "user_type" : "registered",
