    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>As soon as there is only method <code>Long.valueOf(long)</code>, cast from <code>int</code> to <code>long</code> will be done implicitly in case of using <code>Long.valueOf(intValue)</code>.</p>\n\n<p>The more clear way to do this is</p>\n\n<pre><code>Integer.valueOf(intValue).longValue()\n</code></pre>\n"
