    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Suggested From Android Studio lint check : Remove Unnecessary boxing : So, unboxing is :</p>\n<pre><code>public  static  long  integerToLong (int minute ){\n    int delay = minute*1000;\n    long diff = (long) delay;\n    return  diff ; \n}\n</code></pre>\n"
